      <h2 style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: lighter">Collaborative Ownership</h2>
      <p class="large">Collaborate on a common product vision with others as a community team. Earn ownership of the product by completing bounties.</p>

      <hr style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 40px">

      <h2 style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: lighter">Make a Difference</h2>
      <p class="large">Notifications and near-realtime access to finacials, ownership and strategic team decisions so you can guide the direction of the business.</p>

      <hr style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 40px">

      <h2 style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: lighter">Learn While you Build</h2>
      <p class="large">With with others on product and get exposed to new ideas and skills. Participate in the ideation process, web development, visual design or imagining creative revenue opportunity. Grow your existing experience with product.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
